==Titles and honours==
===Titles===
{{Infobox royal styles
|royal name  = King Hussein of Jordan
|image  = [[File:Coat of Arms of Jordan.svg|70px]]
|dipstyle  = His Majesty
|offstyle  = Your Majesty
|altstyle  = ''Sir''}}
* 14 November 1935{{spaced ndash}}20 July 1951: {{em|His Royal Highness}} Prince Hussein of Jordan
* 20 July 1951{{spaced ndash}}11 August 1952: {{em|His Royal Highness}} The Crown Prince of Jordan
* 11 August 1952{{spaced ndash}}7 February 1999: {{em|His Majesty}} The King of the Hashemite Kingdom of Jordan

===Honours===
* [[Jordan]]:
** [[Order of Al-Hussein bin Ali]]<ref name="RArk">{{cite web|url=http://www.royalark.net/Jordan/jordan3.htm|title=Jordanian genealogy details|work=Royal Ark|accessdate=30 June 2017}}</ref>
** [[Supreme Order of the Renaissance]]<ref name="RArk"/>
** [[Order of the Star of Jordan]]<ref name="RArk"/>
** [[Order of Independence]]<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Austria]]:
** Grand Star of the [[Decoration of Honour for Services to the Republic of Austria]] (June 1976)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Bahrain]]:
** Collar of the Order of Khalifa (1976)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Belgium]]:
** Collar of the [[Order of Leopold (Belgium)|Order of Leopold]] (1964)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Brunei]]:
** Collar of the Royal Family Order of the Crown of Brunei (1984)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[China]]:
** Collar special class of the Order of the Propitious Clouds (1959)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Denmark]]:
** Knight of the [[Order of the Elephant]] (27 April 1998)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Egypt]]: 
** Grand Collar of the [[Order of the Nile]] (1955)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Ethiopia]]:
** Knight of the [[Order of Solomon]] of the [[Ethiopian Empire]] (1960)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[France]]:
** Grand Cross of the [[Legion of Honour]] (1967)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Germany]]:
** Grand Cross special class of the [[Order of Merit of the Federal Republic of Germany]] (1967)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Greece]]:
** Grand Cross of the [[Order of the Redeemer]] (1960)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Guinea]]:
** Collar of the Order of National Merit of Guinea (1960)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Holy See]]:
** Knight of the [[Order of the Golden Spur]] of the [[Holy See|Vatican]] (1964)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Iran]]:
** Collar of the [[Order of Pahlavi]] (1959)<ref name="RArk"/>
** Commemorative Medal of the [[2,500 year celebration of the Persian Empire|2500th Anniversary of the founding of the Persian Empire]] (14 October 1971)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Kingdom of Iraq|Iraq]]:
** King Faisal II Coronation Medal (2 May 1953)<ref name="RArk"/>
** Collar of the Grand Order of the Hashemites (1953)<ref name="RArk"/>
** Grand Cordon of the [[Order of the Two Rivers]] (1953)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Italy]]:
** Knight Grand Cross with Collar of the [[Order of Merit of the Italian Republic]] (26 November 1983)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Japan]]:
** Collar of the [[Order of the Chrysanthemum]] (10 March 1976)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Kuwait]]:
** Collar of the [[Order of Mubarak the Great]] (1974)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Lebanon]]:
** Extraordinary class of the [[Order of Merit (Lebanon)|Order of Merit]] of Lebanon  (1960)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Libya]]:
** Collar of the [[Order of Idris I]] (1960)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Malaysia]]:
** Honorary Recipient of the [[Order of the Crown of the Realm]] (1965)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Morocco]]: 
** Collar of the [[Order of Muhammad]] of [[Morocco]] (1960)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Norway]]:
** Knight Grand Cross with Collar of the [[Order of St Olav]] (1964)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Philippines]]:
** Grand Collar of the Ancient [[Order of Sikatuna]] (1 March 1976)<ref name="RArk"/> 
* [[Portugal]]:
** Collar of the [[Order of the Tower and Sword]] (1964)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Qatar]]:
** Collar of the Order of Independence of [[Qatar]] (1978)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Saudi Arabia]]:
** Grand Collar of the [[Order of Abdulaziz al Saud]] (1960)<ref name="RArk"/>
** Collar of the Order of the Badr Chain (1960)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Spain]]: 
** Grand Cross of the [[Crosses of Military Merit (Spain)|Order of Military Merit]], with white distinctive (3 June 1955)<ref name="RArk"/>
** Collar of the [[Order of Isabel the Catholic]] (18 March 1977)<ref name="RArk"/>
** Knight of the [[Order of the Golden Fleece]] (22 March 1985)<ref name="RArk"/>
** [[Prince of Asturias Award]] for Peace (15 September 1995)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Sweden]]:
** Knight of the [[Order of Seraphim]] (15 September 1989)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Syria]]:
** Grand Cordon of the [[Order of Umayyad]] of [[Syria]] (1955)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Netherlands]]:
** Grand Cross of the [[Order of the Netherlands Lion]] (1964)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Tunisia]]:
** Grand Cordon of the Order of Independence of [[Tunisia]] (1956)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[United Kingdom]]:
** Honorary [[Knight Grand Cross of the Royal Victorian Order]] (1953)<ref name="RArk"/>
** Bailiff Grand Cross of the [[Venerable Order of Saint John]] of Jerusalem (1955)<ref name="RArk"/>
** Honorary Knight Grand Cross of the [[Order of the Bath]] (1984)<ref name="RArk"/>
** Recipient of the [[Royal Victorian Chain]] (1966)<ref name="RArk"/>
* [[Yugoslavia]]:
** Great Star of the [[Order of the Yugoslav Star]] (1979)<ref name="RArk"/>

