* [[Kazakhstan]]:
** Street Hussein Bin Talal in [[Astana]]<ref name="joembus">{{cite web|url=http://jordanembassyus.org/news/key-street-astana-named-after-late-king-hussein|title=Key Street in Astana Named After Late King Hussein|work=Petra News Agency|publisher=Jordanian Embassy in Washington DC|accessdate=30 June 2017|date=19 May 2014}}</ref>
* [[Russia]]:
** Park Hussein Bin Talal in [[Grozny]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ammancity.gov.jo/en/resource/snews.asp?id=BA02417A-E9BD-4129-9776-C58E570476A9|title=Deputy Mayor of Amman welcomes a Chechen delegation to discuss strengthening of relations between Amman and Grozny|accessdate=30 June 2017|date=5 March 2011|publisher=[[Greater Amman Municipality]]}}</ref>

